### Set difficulty
PUT {{host}}/api/v2/problems/{{problemId}}/difficulty
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "difficulty": "easy"
}

### Attach tags
POST {{host}}/api/v2/problems/{{problemId}}/tags/attach
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagIds": [
    "{{tagId2}}",
    "{{tagId1}}"
  ]
}

### Replace tags  ( >= 1 Ok)
PUT {{host}}/api/v2/problems/{{problemId}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagIds": [
    "{{tagId1}}"
  ]
}